Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 16:00:49 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] proton: update runtime support for media rework

Carry the remaining runtime and environment support changes needed alongside the winedmo media backend work.

This keeps session helper behavior, loader defaults, prefix registration, and build image assumptions aligned with the Proton media tree after winegstreamer was removed.

No game-specific media workaround is introduced here; the gameplay-visible fixes are documented in the preceding media, SourceReader, Quartz, and audio commits.
---
 dlls/ntdll/unix/loader.c  |  8 --------
 dlls/wtsapi32/wtsapi32.c  |  2 +-
 loader/preloader_mac.c    |  4 ++--
 loader/wine.inf.in        |  2 +-
 tools/gitlab/image.docker | 16 ----------------
 5 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 28 deletions(-)

diff --git a/dlls/ntdll/unix/loader.c b/dlls/ntdll/unix/loader.c
index 022713df20a..3b587133dda 100644
--- a/dlls/ntdll/unix/loader.c
+++ b/dlls/ntdll/unix/loader.c
@@ -2410,14 +2410,6 @@ static void hacks_init(void)
     if (kernel_stack_size != 0x100000)
         ERR( "HACK: setting kernel_stack_size to %luKB.\n", (long)(kernel_stack_size / 1024) );
 
-    if (sgi && (0
-        || !strcmp(sgi, "1364780") || !strcmp(sgi, "1952120") || !strcmp(sgi, "2154900") /* Street Fighter 6 */
-        || !strcmp(sgi, "1740720") /* Have a Nice Death  */
-    ))
-    {
-        ERR("HACK: setting WINE_ENABLE_GST_LIVE_LATENCY.\n");
-        setenv("WINE_ENABLE_GST_LIVE_LATENCY", "1", 0);
-    }
 
     if (sgi && !strcmp(sgi, "2379390"))
     {
